.header3
  .header3__logo
    = link_to root_path do
      .header3__logo__image
    .header3__logo__progress
      = image_tag "step1.png", class: "image", size: "450x35"
.contents3
  .contents3__title
    会員情報入力
  .contents3__entry
    = form_for(@user, url: user_registration_path) do |f|
      = render "devise/shared/error_messages", resource: @user
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "ニックネーム"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.text_field :nickname, placeholder: "例) メルカリ太郎", class: "contents3__form__text"
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "メールアドレス"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.email_field :email, placeholder: "PC・携帯どちらでも可", class: "contents3__form__text", autocomplete: "email"
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "パスワード"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.password_field :password, placeholder: "7文字以上の半角英数字", class: "contents3__form__text", autocomplete: "new-password"
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label :password_confirmation
          %br/
          = f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "new-password"
      .contents3__entry__message1
        ※英字と数字の両方を含めて設定してください
      %p
        %input#js-passcheck{class: "checkbox", type: "checkbox"}
        %label{class: "checkboxMessage", for: "js-passcheck"} パスワードを表示する
      .contents3__entry__passwordResult
        .contents3__entry__passwordResult__string
      .contents3__entry__message3
        本人確認
      .contents3__entry__message4
        安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "お名前(全角)"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.text_field :last_name, placeholder: "例) 山田", class: "contents3__form2__text"
        .field
          %br/
          = f.text_field :first_name, placeholder: "例) 彩", class: "contents3__form2__text"
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "お名前カナ(全角)"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.text_field :last_name_kana, placeholder: "例) ヤマダ", class: "contents3__form2__text"
        .field
          %br/
          = f.text_field :first_name_kana, placeholder: "例) アヤ", class: "contents3__form2__text"
      .contents3__entry__item
        .field
          = f.label "生年月日"
          %span 必須
          %br/
          = f.number_field :birthday_year, class: "contents3__form3__text"
          年
        .field
          %br/
          = f.number_field :birthday_month, class: "contents3__form3__text"
          月
        .field
          %br/
          = f.number_field :birthday_date, class: "contents3__form3__text"
          日
      .contents3__entry__message5
        ※本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
      .contents3__entry__message6
        「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、
        = link_to "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos/" do
          利用規約
        に同意したものとみなします
      .actions
        = f.submit "次へ進む", class: "contents3__btn contents3__btn__next"
      .contents3__entry__message7
        = link_to "https://www.mercari.com/jp/help_center/article/423/" do
          本人情報の登録について〉
      .contents3__entry__message8
        This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the the Google
        = link_to "https://policies.google.com/privacy" do
          Privacy Policy
        and
        = link_to "https://policies.google.com/terms" do
          Terms of Service
        apply.
      .contents3__entry__box



